  characterName: Ninomae Arisa
  description: She's always trying to stay true to her own values no matter what,
    even if it makes herself look a little too serious sometimes. Lightening up isn't
    easy for her, but as Takasu Mitsuko's best friend, she tries to become someone
    more fun to be around. At the same time, she helps Mitsuko keep her head out
    of the clouds.
